        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Octobathynella peelensis gen. nov. sp. nov. (A,B,E,F) Male holotype. (A) Uropod (latero-external view); (B) furcal rami (ventral view); (C) uropod female allotype (latero-external view); (D) furcal rami female allotype (dorsal view); (E) thoracopod VIII (latero-caudal view); (F) thoracopod VIII (latero-frontal view); (G) thoracopod VIII female allotype (ventral view). Scale bar in mm. Abbreviations: D.Lb, dentate lobe: I.Lb, inner lobe; O.Lb, outer lobe; Bsp, basipod; Endp, endopod; Exp, exopod." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4590636/files/figure.png" .

