        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 1. Octobathynella peelensis gen. nov. sp. nov. (A–C,E,F,H–J,K) Male holotype. (A) Antennule (dorsal view); (B) antenna (dorsal view); (C) labrum; (D) labrum of female allotype; (E) distal part of mandible; (F) mandible; (G) mandible of female allotype; (H) maxillule; (I) maxilla; (J) thoracopod VIII (latero-external view); (K) thoracopod VIII (latero-internal view). Scale bar in mm. Abbreviations: D.Lb, dentate lobe: I.Lb, inner lobe; O.Lb, outer lobe; Bsp, basipod; Endp, endopod; Exp, exopod." ;
